casebody.data:
Mohammed Nasser JILANI
v.
Donnie HARRISON, Sheriff Wake County Detention Center No. 139P17-3 Supreme Court of North Carolina. July 11, 2017 Mohammed Nasser Jilani, for Jilani, Mohammed Nasser. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 11th of July 2017 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 11th of July 2017."
